CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776280294
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer 'personally
OL,4,Ccommitted' to bringing in Hillsborough
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has said he is
OL,8,F"personally committed" to delivering a
OL,9,FHillsborough Law, speaking on the 37th
OL,10,Fanniversary of the disaster.
OL,12,FHe told MPs at Prime Minister's
OL,13,FQuestions (PMQs) that he would deliver
OL,14,Fa law that ensures a "duty of candour
OL,15,Fapplies to all public servants" and
OL,16,Fmake sure "the state will always act
OL,17,Ffor the people that it serves."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
