OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776280294
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer 'personally
OL,4,Ccommitted' to bringing in Hillsborough
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FProgress on the Bill stalled last
OL,8,Fyear, after an amendment was pulled
OL,9,Fover concerns that intelligence
OL,10,Fagencies could use it to avoid being
OL,11,Fbound by the proposed duty of candour.
OL,13,FWhat is the Hillsborough Law?
OL,15,FSir Keir insisted all public servants
OL,16,Fwould be covered by the duty of
OL,17,Fcandour at Prime Minister's Questions
OL,18,Fon Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776280294
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer 'personally
OL,4,Ccommitted' to bringing in Hillsborough
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FHis comments came as Ian Byrne, the
OL,8,FLabour MP for Liverpool West Derby,
OL,9,Fquestioned whether victims would "be
OL,10,Ffailed by the state once again".
OL,12,FMr Byrne - who was at Hillsborough
OL,13,Fwhen the disaster happened- said the
OL,14,F97 children, women and men who died
OL,15,Fwere "killed at the hands of a corrupt
OL,16,Fstate".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776280294
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer 'personally
OL,4,Ccommitted' to bringing in Hillsborough
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FHe said to Sir Keir in the Commons:
OL,8,F"As parliamentary lead to the
OL,9,FHillsborough Law, I stand here with a
OL,10,Fhuge sense of obligation to the 97,
OL,11,Fall the families, every survivor and
OL,12,Fevery victim of a state cover-up who
OL,13,Fwere all part of this collective
OL,14,Fcampaign.
OL,16,F"There are signs of progress after
OL,17,Flast night's Government concessions,
OL,18,Fbut we've heard this before.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776280294
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer 'personally
OL,4,Ccommitted' to bringing in Hillsborough
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FMr Byrne told the Prime Minister that
OL,8,Fit is his responsibility to deliver
OL,9,Fthe law, to which he replied that the
OL,10,Fissues are being discussed with the
OL,11,Ffamilies.
OL,13,FHe said at PMQs: "I am personally
OL,14,Fcommitted to working with the families
OL,15,Fto get this Bill right. It is integral
OL,16,Fthat their views are heard.
OL,18,F"I reaffirm my commitment to
OL,19,Fdelivering the legislation to ensuring
OL,20,Fthe duty of candour applies to all
OL,21,Fpublic servants."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776280294
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer 'personally
OL,4,Ccommitted' to bringing in Hillsborough
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FLabour pledged to introduce a
OL,8,FHillsborough Law in its 2024
OL,9,Fmanifesto, but the legislation `
OL,10,Fformally known as the Public Office
OL,11,F(Accountability) Bill ` has stalled
OL,12,Fsince it was introduced in September.
OL,14,FOnce introduced, it would require
OL,15,Fpublic officials to tell the truth
OL,16,Fduring inquiries and investigations,
OL,17,Fhowever progress was stalled over a
OL,18,Fproposed amendment that would see
OL,19,Fspies brought within the scope of the
OL,20,Flaw, but only with the approval of the
OL,21,Fhead of their services.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776280294
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer 'personally
OL,4,Ccommitted' to bringing in Hillsborough
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FCampaigners warned that this could be
OL,8,Fused as a way of escaping the new
OL,9,F"duty of candour" and the amendments
OL,10,Fwere pulled.
OL,12,FDowning Street said the legislation
OL,13,Fwould return to Parliament "soon" but
OL,14,Frefused to commit to bringing it back
OL,15,Fbefore the King's Speech in May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776280294
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer 'personally
OL,4,Ccommitted' to bringing in Hillsborough
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister's official
OL,8,Fspokesman said: "Significant progress
OL,9,Fhas been made over recent weeks,
OL,10,Fworking both with the families and the
OL,11,Fintelligence agencies and we expect to
OL,12,Fbring the Bill back to Parliament
OL,13,Fsoon."
OL,15,FDowning Street said the legislation
OL,16,Fwould return to Parliament "soon" but
OL,17,Frefused to commit to bringing it back
OL,18,Fbefore the King's Speech in May.
OL,26,@xD@\OUxD@aO]
